    </picture>
        <div class="hero-body">
            <div class="container">
                <div class=""><span class="tag is-rounded is-medium blue-grey"> USE CASE </span></div>
                <h1 class="primary-text">Decentralized commercial lease agreements</h1>
                <h2 class="dark-indigo">Legal documents are still static pieces of paper. Live Contracts achieve unique automation and efficiency.</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top">
    <section class="section secondary promo-numbers-section">
        <div class="promo-numbers c">
