                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">The building passport</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Especially new buildings can start 'the right way' by creating a building passport. When selling a building, a complete and trusted set of data is transferred. Transferring buildings with LTO Network assures a full, trusted collection of data when switching owners.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter lazy" data-bg="url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')"  style="left:48px;height:250px;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:30px;top: 100px;left: -90px;" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:50px;top: 200px;left: 230px;" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:90px;position:relative; top:0px; left:73px;" data-src="/assets/icons/diagram.svg" alt="LTO Network - Ease of integration">
                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Ease of integration</h3>
                    <p class="muted">LTO Network is a fully decentralized and highly efficient blockchain infrastructure that is easy to integrate into existing (legacy) systems, mobile applications, and IoT devices. LTO Network is production-ready for instant efficiency upgrades.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter lazy" data-bg="url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')"  style="left:48px;height:250px;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:30px;top: 230px;left: 200px;" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width: 70px;top: 9px;left: -100px;" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
