                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Liquidity</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Liquidity improvement, making fewer write-offs on tenants who go bankrupt. Through Live Contracts, service charges can be debited directly instead of months after the close of the year through smart payments. </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="table-container is-centered has-margin-top-40">
